name: Observation Perch
description:
A Black-Capped Chickadee is perched on a branch and investigates its surroundings to find something to eat on a bright snowy day.

2017. Nikon D60, 55-200mm Lens.

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing.

Birb Series: Part 1 - Chickadee I
